# جمر (Jamr) — Restaurant Landing Page

A fully RTL Arabic landing page for a fictional charcoal-grill restaurant concept.

## Features
- Full RTL layout with logical CSS properties
- Arabic typography (Cairo / Lalezar)
- Full-bleed responsive hero section
- Menu section with pricing cards (Eastern Arabic numerals)
- Fully responsive: mobile, tablet, and desktop

## Stack
HTML5 · Tailwind CSS

